	(text "Tsumikoro ESP32 RS-485 Bridge — rev 0.1\n\nPower: sourced from either JBUS1 or JBUS2 pin 1 (bus V+),\nregulated to 3.3V by the LMR38020 sub-sheet (see PSU).\n\nNo local JPWR — board is bus-powered only.\n\nESP32 DevKitC-V4 plugs into two 1x19 female headers\n(J_ESP_L / J_ESP_R) spaced 22.86 mm apart (1 inch row pitch)."
		(at 25 25 0)
		(effects (font (size 2 2)) (justify left))
	)

